    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent performance and aesthetic integrity. This unit has undergone a rigorous inspection process to ensure it meets our standards for mechanical reliability and cabin preservation. With a documented service history and a commitment to quality, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to evaluate this exceptional offering in person.",
      "price": 35900.0,
